<dl id="n53123ab"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n53" href="#n53123ab">N53 (VI.B.46)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n53all.htm#n53123ab"> 123(ab)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> salute 7 times, <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="n53123ab"><li>FW 26.09 </li><li><a href="../../flex/a/lexa.htm#n53123ab">2010</a> </li><li><a href="../../flex/a/l39a.htm#n53123ab">1939</a> </li><li><ms href="#n53123ab">MS BL 47476a-149</ms> </li><li>JJA 49:321 <a name="ad7" href="../../ff/fdra/ada.htm#ad7">Usage</a> </li><li> <a href="../../flex/a/ad7.htm#n53123ab">Draft: I.1&sect;1.7</a>/2.7</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">Il entra. La maison fut toute illumin&eacute;e. Souj&acirc;t&acirc;, pour l&apos;honorer, <mark>le salua par sept fois</mark>. Il s&apos;assit. Souj&acirc;t&acirc; se mit &agrave; genoux et lui lava les pieds avec de l&apos;eau parfum&eacute;e, puis elle lui tendit le vase d&apos;or, plein de lait &agrave; la farine et de riz au miel. <small> A. Ferdinand Herold, <a name="AFHB" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#AFHB"><cite title="source">La Vie Du Bouddha</cite></a> (1922) 79</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: When he came back to the village on the day following the night of the five dreams, Siddharta met Soujata and she saluted him seven times and gave him hot milk, honey, and rice in a golden bowl. </mm> </dd></dl>
